sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant API
    participant DB

    Browser->>+API: POST /login (credentials)
    API->>API: Validate input
    API->>+DB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?
    DB-->>-API: User record
    alt User found
        API->>API: Compare password hash
        alt Password matches
            API->>+DB: INSERT session token
            DB-->>-API: OK
            API-->>Browser: 200 OK + JWT
        else Password wrong
            API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        end
    else User not found
        API-->>-Browser: 404 Not Found
    end
    Note over Browser,API: Subsequent requests use JWT
    Browser->>+API: GET /profile (JWT)
    API->>+DB: SELECT profile WHERE user_id = ?
    DB-->>-API: Profile data
    API-->>-Browser: 200 OK + profile JSON
